The paper deals with the capacity of cellular wireless networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The use of Poisson point processes and power control strategies suggests a focus on mathematical analysis (cs.MA) and system design (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the limitations of the network, which could fall under the category of performance evaluation (cs.PF).
